{"tid":187481,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[日本] 毒遊東京 10日行程求教","createTime":"2017-04-05T04:05:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-22T00:47:35.000Z","uid":84628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c89d6c8cfa6d93c1b08d05f7984194caa12ca179","tid":187481,"uid":84628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T04:05:35.000Z","msg":"小弟黎緊五月中打算一條友去日本旅行，暫時機票同酒店都未BOOK，人生第一次去咁遠既地方，所以ＰＯＳＴ上黎問下各位巴絲有咩建議<br />\n<br />\n行程如下<br />\n<br />\n1\t\t\t羽田/成田機場 --&gt; ?<br />\n2\t\t\t築地市場<br />\n2\t\t台場\t台場海濱公園<br />\n2\t\t台場\tLego Land + 富士電視台 + Diver city<br />\n2\t\t台場\t未來科學館<br />\n2\t\t台場\t大江戶溫泉<br />\n3\t\t上野\t上野公園 or 上野動物園<br />\n3\t\t上野\t阿美橫丁<br />\n3\t\t淺草\t淺草寺(閒日)<br />\n3\t\t淺草\t淺草仲見世通 -&gt; 淺草文化觀光中心<br />\n3\t\t淺草\tSKYTREE<br />\n4\t\t橫濱\t山手西洋館<br />\n4\t\t橫濱\t山下公園/大棧橋-&gt;紅磚倉庫&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\n4\t\t橫濱\tCUP NODDLE MUSEUM<br />\n4\t\t橫濱\tQueen Square<br />\n4\t\t橫濱\t橫濱地標大廈<br />\n5\t\t\t鐮倉 + 江之島<br />\n6\t\t原宿\t竹下通&nbsp;&rarr;&nbsp;表參道 &rarr;&nbsp;表參道之丘<br />\n6\t\t原宿\t明治神宮<br />\n6\t\t澀谷\tHIKARIE &rarr; SHIBUYA 109<br />\n7\t\t\t吉卜力美術館<br />\n7\t\t\t吉祥寺<br />\n7\t\t\t東京站<br />\n7\t\t\t東京中央郵便局<br />\n7\t\t\t東京丸之內<br />\n8\t\t新宿\t新宿御苑&nbsp;<br />\n8\t\t新宿\t東京都廳<br />\n8\t\t新宿\t行下街<br />\n9\t\t\t箱根&nbsp;<br />\n10\t\t\t???<br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n上網爬完文暫時PLAN到咁多<br />\n當然有D地方係見到但唔知點PLAN<br />\n<br />\nSunshine City水族館<br />\n六本木hills City View<br />\n银座<br />\n國營昭和記念公園&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n唔該晒巴絲們比意見 交通 飲食方面既都講得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"066c080c4edbc322a5120486fbc62f3a2781eee6","tid":187481,"uid":84628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T05:13:55.000Z","msg":"有冇日本達人解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eedfe5faa7267167cc4ace0809c7d7679b806cd8","tid":187481,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T07:58:47.000Z","msg":"五月中去仲未book機票酒店？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63964f509cae5c68c1a68df4632b1bd005679760","tid":187481,"uid":84628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T08:36:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>五月中去仲未book機票酒店？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n酒店方面有冇咩地區方便我依個行程? 見D人推薦上野/新宿<br />\n想查清楚先BOOK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f954f1eea032981102813404b3332e9d0211f004","tid":187481,"uid":87780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T02:00:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>五月中去仲未book機票酒店？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n酒店方面有冇咩地區方便我依個行程? 見D人推薦上野/新宿<br />\n想查清楚先BOOK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇錢咪新宿9 hour <br />\n有錢咪apa果啲"},{"pid":"490c8be0ef2f0231281b5a9a137eb5f30f982c23","tid":187481,"uid":46388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T02:05:09.000Z","msg":"10日都係東京內 比我會悶死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bfde523285b652bf90534750e3635fc564dc95a","tid":187481,"uid":35586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T06:54:53.000Z","msg":"人在新宿，無plan過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n尋日去完阿美橫町黎，可以慳返唔洗去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c42baf7c61f91e3a8bb5f9ada4789798103900e9","tid":187481,"uid":63825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"490c8be0ef2f0231281b5a9a137eb5f30f982c23","tid":187481,"uid":46388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T02:05:09.000Z","msg":"10日都係東京內 比我會悶死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T00:47:35.000Z","msg":"8月去東京 10日應該點攪？"}]}